cs.CR, cs.IR, cs.CY, cs.SI, cs.DC 

This paper discusses the privacy issues in the Internet of Things, which involves the management of personal data and tracking and profiling. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CR (Cryptography and Security). The paper also discusses the evolving features and trends in the Internet of Things, which could fall under cs.IR (Information Retrieval) and cs.SI (Social and Information Networks). Additionally, the paper examines the challenges that need to be overcome, which could fall under cs.CY (Computers and Society) and cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing).
